SAFA's obsession with muthi, inyangas and herbalists has made a mockery of our football. After being embroiled in a protracted payment dispute with Sibonelo Madela, a traditional healer from Ulundi in KwaZulu-Natal who had threatened to prevent Bafana from winning matches, Safa started courting the services of Eastern Cape herbalist Reuben Matewu after the goalless draw against Cape Verde last Saturday. Stop the mumbo jumbo and address the problems in the Bafana camp, you moegoes!